    "The four cofounders were previously working at Indian e-commerce outfit Flipkart.",
    "Bengaluru-based Groww has more than 50 million customers and two-thirds of them are under 35.",
    "The company's IPO in November 2025 raised $83 million and made Keshre a billionaire."
